echo.
echo SORT is short for Simple Open-source Ray Tracing. It is a stand along cross platform
echo physically based renderer. It is my personal side project that I have been working
echo on ever since 2011. Following are features supported in SORT renderer so far,
echo:
echo    * Path Tracing, Bidirectional Path Tracing, Light Tracing, Instant Radiosity,
echo      Ambient Occlusion, Whitted Ray Tracing.
echo    * KD-Tree, BVH, OcTree, Uniform Grid.
echo    * Point Light, Spot Light, Directional Light, Area Light, HDR Image Based Lighting.
echo    * Disney BRDF (2015), Lambert, LambertTransmission, Oran Nayar, Microfacet Reflection,
echo      Microfacet Tranmission, MERL Measured BRDF, Fourier BRDF, AshikhmanShirley BRDF,
echo      Phong, Coat, Blend, Double-Sided, Ditribution BRDF, DreamWorks' Fabric BRDF.
echo    * Sursurface Scattering.
echo    * Hair, Fur.
echo    * Open Shading Language.
echo    * Depth of Field.
echo    * Multi-threaded Rendering.
echo    * Blender 2.8.
echo:
